Active device users refer to users with an 'active' status in the device_users table; 
Sensor id 0 represents the heart rate sensor; 
value_x in the readings table represents the heart rate measurement.

- 'fuel level' refers to 'battery level'; 
- 'vehicles' refers to 'devices'; 
- 'running smoothly' refers to 'status = active' in the devices table; 
- 'people who are always on the move' refers to users with 'activity level = active'.
